I think this blueprint has to be aligned.

772
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:27,200
Yes.

773
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:27,840
Something to look forward to.

774
00:28:27,840 --> 00:28:29,400
You need something
to look forward to in dating.

775
00:28:29,400 --> 00:28:31,400
I'm dating you because I want

776
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:32,440
